{"tid":2258100,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"cuscs 上莊對升學係咪有幫助","createTime":"2020-10-25T17:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T12:33:46.000Z","uid":365536,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cf21fb28c7d65e27e3fd32de9c0f4dd743bef1db","tid":2258100,"uid":365536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daed311981ae923c11dee9ecaac73cc32a124861","tid":2258100,"uid":110719,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:52:00.000Z","msg":"入左去應該絕望"},{"pid":"1b428179a0f5a87309064cf1925338edcbb2fb5e","tid":2258100,"uid":11506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:53:21.000Z","msg":"係 上多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f4a18871122c43e1cc102f0e4747eb7214c09e","tid":2258100,"uid":312205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:54:01.000Z","msg":"你覺得會有咩幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d535a106a05a85fda30b6950bc842d15fa608355","tid":2258100,"uid":9392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:56:44.000Z","msg":"長上啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"4559fb55e9a8875ac42006ded221a392f8b0ea5b","tid":2258100,"uid":5065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:58:33.000Z","msg":"咪撚傻，學店嚟咋傻鳩"},{"pid":"f7aefeffad83988e2db15ba829ff63efc6e6e971","tid":2258100,"uid":327934,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:02:38.000Z","msg":"關於上莊識多啲人呢個講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSorry，想引用大陸文章<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為覺得講得好中肯<br />\n<br />\n「沒有硬實力，人脈就是個笑話<br />\n<br />\n當孫悟空還是猴子的時候，只能和一群猴子玩。<br />\n<br />\n當他學了一身本領之後，他就可以和牛魔王稱兄道弟，還可以跟龍王呼來喝去搶寶貝！<br />\n<br />\n大鬧天宮之前，巨靈神都不把他放在眼裏，大鬧天宮之後，天庭總參謀長托塔李天王都對他畢恭畢敬！<br />\n<br />\n到雷音寺之前，他對菩薩只能頂禮膜拜，等成了鬥戰聖佛之後，和菩薩成了哥們。<br />\n<br />\n孫悟空的的故事告訴我們：只有當你強大時，才會吸引到更高層的人脈關係！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290dd6b59695311d48265e7fb834a7e2d57d58b7","tid":2258100,"uid":365536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7f4a18871122c43e1cc102f0e4747eb7214c09e","tid":2258100,"uid":312205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:54:01.000Z","msg":"你覺得會有咩幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:10:41.000Z","msg":"我覺得冇 但身邊嘅人為咗有助升學而上莊  唔明🥱"},{"pid":"6b145262001b5e2d2713c4a5cf144353fd815b65","tid":2258100,"uid":365536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daed311981ae923c11dee9ecaac73cc32a124861","tid":2258100,"uid":110719,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:52:00.000Z","msg":"入左去應該絕望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:11:01.000Z","msg":"何出此言呢"},{"pid":"2b27f10c53c3ece532f67658ba1ffcf1a62d81dd","tid":2258100,"uid":40867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:12:06.000Z","msg":"問得嘅都係智障<br />\n<br />\n答你都救你唔到"},{"pid":"dc96a234cac4d1e35867b2d40048072a7ce21686","tid":2258100,"uid":217385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:33:46.000Z","msg":"有助你學識1分鐘make3個decisions"}]}